It looks as described and like the pic...i just didn't care for it for me. It looked more like a curly afro puff almost on me.
I like the bangs. If they made this in a body wave or thick curls, it would be nice also.
If this could be made in different textures and curl type it would be great.. it would give us choices. Review Title: Not for me but you might love it. Rating: 4.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Long lasting Eyebrow pencil with Brown Brow Gel for Tattoo Eyes Makeup Fine Sketch Natural Hair-Like Review Date: 2018/11/01 Store: YRYM HT Average Rating: 3.5 Product Details: {'Brand': 'YRYM HT', 'Item Form': 'Gel,Pencil', 'Finish Type': 'Natural', 'Special Feature': 'Long Lasting', 'Material Feature': 'Natural', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Package Dimensions': '5 x 1 x 0.45 inches; 0.63 Ounces', 'UPC': '700401120498'} Review Text: It.s like a marker not pencil. If you mess up and it dries it will not whipe off. You have to use soap or alcohol several times. You have to be very very light-handed for this or it.ll look crazy.
This needs to be made out of a pencil not marker and it.ll be nice. Review Title: I didn't like that it.s a marker. Rating: 3.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Magic Collection 3.5 Inch Wide Band Bonnet Elastic Band Black Review Date: 2020/11/01 Store: Magic Collection Average Rating: 4.5 Product Details: {'Color': 'Black', 'Age Range (Description)': 'Adult', 'Number of Items': '1', 'Brand': 'Magic Collection', 'Size': '3.5 Inch (Pack of 1)', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Package Dimensions': '8.39 x 4.88 x 0.59 inches; 1.59 Ounces', 'Item model number': 'SG_B07345F1BX_US', 'UPC': '636227221951'} Review Text: ☆Make SURE you wash this before wearing it. I did not and there were huge dye stains on my pillows. I ended up washing it... there was so much dye in the sink..the water was darker than this... like, Black when I started washing it. I was running water the whole time I was washing it so the water looks like a light purple but it didn.t start that way, the water was nearly jet black at first.
With that said,..I like the band around it..it.s big and spacious as well.

Update...i.ve had to wash it again and again as the stains were still getting on my white pillowcases. The dye for this thing is really strong as it doesn't wash out easily. It can.t be all that safe having that dye seep into your scalp which, seeps into your body/system.
I don.t sleep in it anymore...I just wear it during the day at home when I want my hair out of the way. I ended up buying a white one and that 1 works better for me. Review Title: Wash It Before Wearing! Rating: 4.0 --------------------------------------------------

- **Makeup and Beauty Tools:** The individual exhibits a strong interest in quality makeup brushes and tools, favoring items that are durable and long-lasting. Positive reviews indicate satisfaction with performance and aesthetics, particularly regarding color and material.

- **Hair Care Products:** The person shows a preference for hair products that provide hold and control, especially tinted edge control gel. There’s an appreciation for effectiveness, underscored by a highly favorable review.

- **Avoiding Markers for Eyebrow Products:** A distinct mention illustrates dissatisfaction with eyebrow products that apply like a marker, suggesting a preference for traditional pencil formats.

- **Cautious with Accessories:** There is a notable concern about product safety and hygiene, particularly with headwear that may stain or irritate, highlighting a careful approach to hair accessories.

- **Brand Loyalty:** Frequent interactions with established brands indicate trust and preference for specific names in the beauty category.

Overall, this person's purchasing behavior reflects a commitment to quality beauty tools, effective hair care solutions, and a cautious approach to new products.

There needs to be more hair on it especially at the top.
Also, the little sack/bag Your hair actually goes in doesn't stretch much ...I have a lot of hair and thick hair..it literally doesn't stretch all the way over my bun and I have been buying these ponytails since the 90s.
I hate that you can see the tracks. I.m going to end up throwing it away.
